                        "body": "<div class=\"u-mt-4\">\n<div class=\"u-mt-3 u-font-bold u-mb-3\">User notes:</div>\n<div class=\"u-mt-3 u-mb-3 u-italic\"><span class=\"u-italic\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">About this chapter:</span> Mechanical systems are a key element of any <span class=\"u-italic\">building</span>. Chapter 28 regulates such systems by linking to the </span><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/imc-2024\">Mechanical Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\"><i>of New York State </i></span><span class=\"u-italic\">and </span><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ifgc-2024\">Fuel Gas Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span>, <span class=\"u-italic\">where details of mechanical system requirements are provided.</span></div>\n</div>",
