                                        "amendType": "edit",
                                        "ancestorRefs": [
                                            "28",
                                            "2801"
                                        ],
                                        "body": "<div>The provisions of this chapter, the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/imc-2024\">Mechanical Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span> and the <span class=\"u-italic\">Fuel Gas <span class=\"code_addition\">Code of New York State</span></span> shall govern the design, construction, erection and installation of mechanical appliances, equipment and systems used in <span class=\"u-italic\">buildings</span> and <span class=\"u-italic\">structures</span> covered by this code. <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#masonry_\">Masonry</a> <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#chimney_\">chimneys</a>, <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#fireplace_\">fireplaces</a> and barbecues shall comply with the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/imc-2024\">Mechanical Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span> and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/21/masonry#21\">Chapter 21</a> of this code. The <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ifc-2024\">Fire Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span>, the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ipmc-2024\">Property Maintenance Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span>, the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/imc-2024\">Mechanical Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span> and the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ifgc-2024\">Fuel Gas Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span> shall govern the use and maintenance of mechanical components, appliances, equipment and systems. The<span class=\"u-italic\"> <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/iebc-2024\">Existing Building Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span>, the<span class=\"u-italic\"> <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/imc-2024\">Mechanical Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span> and the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ifgc-2024\">Fuel Gas Code</a> <span class=\"code_addition\">of New York State</span></span> shall govern the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#alteration_\">alteration</a></span>, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#repair_\">repair</a></span>, relocation, replacement and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/new_york/ibc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#addition_\">addition</a> of mechanical components, appliances, equipment and systems.</div>",
