                                                "imageType": "svg"
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "key": "duct_covering_penetrations",
                                                "title": "Duct Coverings: Penetration of Assemblies Prohibited",
                                                "descriptionHtml": "<div>Where a wall or floor with a required fire-resistance rating is penetrated by a duct, the duct covering is not allowed to penetrate the wall or floor.  Where a wall or floor that is required to be fireblocked is penetrated by a duct, the duct covering is not allowed to penetrate the wall or floor.</div>",
